      <title>Version 0.1.10</title>
      <description><![CDATA[Patch: text selection, overlay sizing, test fixes.

• Text selection now works reliably on all machines — Cmd+C fallback uses clipboard polling (up to 300ms) instead of a fixed 100ms wait that was too short for Chrome on slower systems.
