    <item>
      <title>Version 0.1.12</title>
      <description><![CDATA[Text selection: delegate to SelectedTextKit's full strategy chain for broader app compatibility.

• Replaced custom Cmd+C fallback with SelectedTextKit's shortcut strategy (5ms polling, 400ms timeout, muted alert, robust clipboard handling).
• Kept fast AX query + Chrome/Electron AX activation as first steps.
• Should improve detection on apps where our custom Cmd+C was failing.]]></description>
