    <item>
      <title>Version 0.1.13</title>
      <description><![CDATA[Fix: text selection now works universally — Chrome, Slack, Claude desktop, Numbers, and all other apps.

• Root cause: the unified hotkey used a fast AX-only check that skipped the full fallback chain (AX tree activation, Edit→Copy menu action, Cmd+C simulation). Apps without native AX text support always fell through to dictation.
• Now: fast AX peek first, then full fallback chain before deciding. ~500ms delay in the "no selection" case for non-native-AX apps; instant for native apps.
• Added detailed diagnostic logging ([SEL] [DIAG]) for future debugging.]]></description>
